{"word":"G3143 - μαρτύρομαι - martýromai - mar-too'-rom-ahee - Take to record","slug":"G3143","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μαρτύρομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>martýromai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mar-too'-rom-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Take to record"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03C1;&#x03C4;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - marturomai</b> - <i>mar-too'-rom-ahee</i><p/>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G3144\">G3144</a>; to <i>be adduced</i> as <i>a witness</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>obtest</i> (in affirmation or exhortation): - take to record, testify."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1263\">G1263</a>, <a href=\"#/G1957\">G1957</a>, <a href=\"#/G2649\">G2649</a>, <a href=\"#/G3140\">G3140</a>, <a href=\"#/G3141\">G3141</a>, <a href=\"#/G3142\">G3142</a>, <a href=\"#/G3144\">G3144</a>, <a href=\"#/G4303\">G4303</a>, <a href=\"#/G4828\">G4828</a>, <a href=\"#/G4901\">G4901</a>, <a href=\"#/G5575\">G5575</a>, <a href=\"#/G5576\">G5576</a>, <a href=\"#/G5577\">G5577</a>"}]}